high_descs: Turn left and go straight towards the wall. Then, hang left and walk straight into the room and turn to the dining table on your right
Pick up lettuce from the dining table
Turn around and head straight, then proceed to turn left towards the sink
Place lettuce on the sink
Go left and head straight towards the wall. After that, turn left and walk straight into the room, turning to the sink on your right
Pick up butter knife from the sink
Head straight towards the table by turning around and turning left
Place lettuce on the table
anns.task_desc: Obtaining lettuce from various locations and arranging them in a table

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the farther part of the diningtable before facing it.
Pick up a lettuce from the diningtable.
Turn right and step forward to be within the reach of a sink table.
Place the lettuce on the sink table.
Come close to the sink table and take a tiny step to the right.
Pick up a butterknife from the sink table.
Go back to your previous position near the sink table.
Cut the lettuce on the sink table using the butterknife.
anns.task_desc: Cut the lettuce on the sink table with the butterknife.

high_descs: Turn around and face towards the dining table
Pick up the lettuce from the table
Turn left and walk to the kitchen sink
Set the lettuce down on the counter left of the sink
Move slightly to the right and face towards the sink
Pick up the butter knife from the counter top
Move slightly left and face the lettuce on the counter top
Use the knife to slice the lettuce on the counter top
anns.task_desc: Put the lettuce on the counter and slice it with a knife
